    "The former is probably due to the training method of LLMs, which focuses on its capability to summarize documents and paraphrase paragraphs.",
    "The latter is due to the inclusion of general medical knowledge in the training data.",
    "Specifically, in the category of summarization, summarizing medical notes is the type of task in which LLMs were applied the most.",
